('B2',3,'essay','opinion_essay','Write 4 sentences of an opinion essay on technology.',NULL,'Technology undoubtedly shapes modern life. While it offers unprecedented convenience, it also raises ethical concerns. Moreover, it transforms the workplace at a dizzying pace. Ultimately, we must wield it with wisdom.','Use formal register.','elevated vocabulary.',120),
('B2',3,'essay','argument_essay','Argue a position with concessions (4 sentences).',NULL,'Admittedly, remote work has drawbacks such as isolation. Nevertheless, its benefits far outweigh these concerns. Not only does it save commuting time, but it also boosts productivity. In light of this, companies should embrace flexibility.','Use concession + strong argument.','admittedly, nevertheless, not only.',120),
('B2',3,'essay','formal_report','Write the introduction of a formal report (4 sentences).',NULL,'This report examines the impact of remote work on productivity. Data was collected from 500 employees across three sectors. The findings are presented in three sections. Recommendations are outlined at the end.','Use passive and formal tone.','passive voice and headings.',120),
('B2',3,'essay','inversion_advanced','Write 4 sentences with advanced inversion.',NULL,'Not only had he lied, but he had also stolen. Hardly had the meeting started when the fire alarm rang. Under no circumstances should you share the password. Little did she realize how much he cared.','Use varied inversions.','negative adverbs triggering inversion.',120),
('B2',3,'essay','idioms_advanced','Use 4 advanced idioms in context.',NULL,'He threw in the towel after the third attempt. She hit the nail on the head with her analysis. They are skating on thin ice financially. It is time to face the music.','Use idioms naturally.','throw in the towel, face the music.',120),
('B2',3,'essay','cleft_emphasis','Write 4 complex cleft sentences for emphasis.',NULL,'What strikes me most is the complexity. It was only after years of work that she succeeded. The reason why we failed is lack of planning. All that we need is more time.','Use varied cleft structures.','what, it, reason, all + cleft.',120),
('B2',3,'essay','subjunctive_formal','Write 4 formal sentences using subjunctive.',NULL,'The committee recommended that the proposal be rejected. It is imperative that he attend the meeting. The law requires that every vehicle be insured. I suggest he apply immediately.','Use bare infinitive.','formal mandative subjunctive.',120),
