('C1',1,'essay','academic_essay','Write an academic introduction (4 sentences).',NULL,'This paper examines the effects of globalization on local cultures. Drawing on recent research, it identifies three main patterns. It argues that cultural homogenization is less inevitable than often assumed. The implications for policy are considered in the conclusion.','Use academic register.','academic tone and structure.',120),
