('C1',1,'essay','complex_syntax','Use 4 complex sentence structures.',NULL,'Having considered the options, we opted for the hybrid approach. Given the circumstances, this seems reasonable. Such was his influence that policy changed. Not only did she lead, but she also inspired.','Use participles, inversions, given + noun.','varied complex structures.',120),
