('C1',1,'essay','formal_register','Write 4 sentences in highly formal register.',NULL,'We would be most grateful for your prompt attention to this matter. Further details may be provided upon request. Should you have any queries, please do not hesitate to contact us. We appreciate your continued support.','Use formal collocations.','would be grateful, should you have.',120),
('C1',1,'essay','reported_speech_advanced','Report 4 statements with advanced structures.',NULL,'She admitted to having made the error. He denied any involvement in the scheme. The committee acknowledged that reforms were needed. The witness confirmed having seen the incident.','Use reporting verbs + structures.','admit/deny + gerund/noun.',120),
('C1',1,'essay','cleft_emphasis','Use cleft sentences to emphasize (4 sentences).',NULL,'It is precisely this approach that distinguishes our method. What ultimately matters is the long-term impact. The fundamental issue is one of trust. All that remains is to reach consensus.','Use varied cleft structures.','it is, what, the Y is, all that.',120),
