('C1',2,'essay','academic_argument','Present an academic argument (4 sentences).',NULL,'This essay contends that urbanization poses significant challenges to sustainability. While recognizing its economic benefits, the analysis highlights environmental costs. Drawing on empirical data, three key issues emerge. The paper concludes with policy recommendations.','Use academic register.','contend, highlight, conclude.',120),
