('C1',3,'essay','dissertation','Write a 4-sentence dissertation abstract.',NULL,'This dissertation interrogates the intersection of technology and democracy. Employing mixed-methods research, it analyzes data from three national contexts. The findings challenge prevailing assumptions about digital participation. The study concludes by proposing a revised theoretical framework.','Use academic abstract register.','interrogate, employ, challenge, propose.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','critical_analysis','Write a critical analysis (4 sentences).',NULL,'The authors central claim, while provocative, lacks empirical grounding. Key evidence is either anecdotal or drawn from limited samples. Moreover, the methodology obscures rather than clarifies the relationship. Consequently, the conclusions should be treated with considerable caution.','Use evaluative academic language.','provocative, empirical, obscure.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','policy_recommendation','Write 4 policy recommendations.',NULL,'It is imperative that policymakers adopt a long-term perspective. We recommend that funding be ring-fenced for preventive measures. Moreover, it is essential that stakeholders be consulted throughout. Finally, regular independent evaluations should be mandated.','Use formal recommendations.','imperative, ring-fence, mandate.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','hedged_claim','Write 4 carefully hedged claims about research.',NULL,'The evidence would suggest a correlation, though causation remains unproven. These results could, in principle, be explained by multiple factors. It seems plausible that cultural variables play a role. Further investigation is, arguably, warranted.','Use advanced hedging.','would suggest, in principle, plausible, arguably.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','review','Write a 4-sentence academic review.',NULL,'This volume offers a comprehensive treatment of a neglected subject. The author marshals an impressive array of sources to support her thesis. Nevertheless, certain chapters would benefit from sharper argumentation. On balance, the book is a welcome contribution to the field.','Use balanced reviewing language.','marshal, benefit from, on balance.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','subjunctive_advanced','Write 4 sentences with advanced subjunctive.',NULL,'It is essential that the protocol be followed without exception. We propose that the deadline be extended by two weeks. Be that as it may, the decision has been made. Suffice it to say, the outcome was unexpected.','Use subjunctive structures.','be that as it may, suffice it to say.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','cleft_elegant','Write 4 elegant cleft sentences.',NULL,'What lies at the heart of the issue is a fundamental disagreement. It was not until the final hour that consensus was reached. The very foundation of the argument is empirical. All that is required is political will.','Use sophisticated cleft.','lies at heart, not until, very foundation.',120),
('C1',3,'essay','register_high','Write 4 sentences in highly formal register.',NULL,'We are pleased to acknowledge receipt of your esteemed correspondence. Kindly accept our sincere apologies for the delay in responding. Should further clarification be required, we remain at your disposal. We look forward to our continued collaboration.','Use elevated formal style.','esteemed, sincere, at your disposal.',120),
